    "history_delete_unit_btn": "Goge wannan unit da unrukuni its albarkatu (albarkatu su ne kept).",
    "history_filter_unit_select": "Tace history list zuwa nuna only albarkatu daga na musamman unit.",
    "history_item_drag": "Ja wannan albarkatu zuwa reorder it ko matsa it zuwa different unit.",
